TextEng: Who are you?
Who you be?
I want to ask you some questions.
Me want ask question.
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
I'm sorry, I don't understand you.
Me no understand.
What are you trying to say?
Huh?
I'll be going now.
Me go now.
What can you tell me about the Creator Race?
Text: 창조자 종족에 대해 알려줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: What you know 'bout Creator Race?
What is this place you are building?
What you build here?
I am searching for one of the Words of Power.
Text: 권능의 언령 중 하나를 찾고 있어요.

TextEng: Me look for Power Word.
What can you tell me about these golem guardians?
Text: 이 수호 골렘에 대해 알려줄 수 있어요?

TextEng: You know more 'bout golems?
What was that you said about magical wards?
What you say 'bout magic wards?
Do you know what the vault protects?
What be inside vault?
Thank you for your help. I will be going now.
Me thank you for help. Me go now.
I've changed my mind. I want you to make the golem vulnerable to fire instead.
Text: 생각이 바뀌었어요. 대신 골렘을 화염에 약하게 만들어줘요.

TextEng: I've changed my mind. I want you to make the golem vulnerable to cold instead.
Text: 생각이 바뀌었어요. 대신 골렘을 냉기에 약하게 만들어줘요.

TextEng: I've changed my mind. I want you to make the golem vulnerable to blunt weapons instead.
Text: 생각이 바뀌었어요. 대신 골렘을 둔기에 약하게 만들어줘요.

TextEng: I've changed my mind. I want you to make the golem vulnerable to slashing and piercing weapons.
Text: 생각이 바뀌었어요. 골렘을 참격과 관통 무기에 약하게 만들어줘요.

TextEng: Me change mind. Make golem hurt by cold now, 'kay?
Text: 나 생각 바뀌었어. 골렘 냉기에 약하게 해줘, 응?

TextEng: Me change mind. Make golem hurt by blunt weapons now, 'kay?
Text: 나 생각 바뀌었어. 골렘 둔기에 약하게 해줘, 응?

TextEng: Me change mind. Make golem hurt by slashing 'n' piercing weapons now, 'kay?
Text: 나 생각 바뀌었어. 골렘 베고 찌르는 거에 약하게 해줘, 응?

TextEng: Me change mind. Make golem hurt by fire now, 'kay?
Text: 나 생각 바뀌었어. 골렘 불에 약하게 해줘, 응?

TextEng: Tell me more about this vault and these golems.
Me want know more about vault and golems.
Text: 나 금고랑 골렘 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Is there any way I could convince you not to finish building the golem?
Text: 골렘을 완성하지 않게 설득할 수 있을까요?

TextEng: You no finish golem.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I could free you from your enslavement.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> I could give you gold. Lots of it!
Here is Lokar's ring. He said you would help me.
Text: 여기 로카의 반지예요. 도와줄 거라고 했어요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me help you escape!
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 너 탈출 도와줄 수 있어!

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Me give you big gold.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 나 금화 많이 줄 수 있어.

TextEng: Me got Lokar ring. Him say you help.
Text: 나 로카 반지 있어. 그가 도와줄 거라 했어.

TextEng: Please, if you help me it will strike a great blow against the tyranny of the Creator Race that has enslaved you.
Text: 부탁이에요, 도와주면 당신을 노예로 삼은 창조자 종족의 폭정에 큰 타격을 줄 거예요.

TextEng: You help me it be bad for lizard folk who make you slave.
Text: 너 나 도와주면 너 노예로 삼은 도마뱀 놈들한테 안 좋아.

TextEng: Fire.
Cold.
Blunt weapons.
Slashing and piercing weapons.
I am not an escaped slave! I am visitor from the distant future.
Text: 저는 탈출한 노예가 아니에요! 먼 미래에서 온 방문자예요.

TextEng: Me not slave! Me come from future!
Text: 나 노예 아냐! 나 미래에서 왔어!
